      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a precision 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring neutral handling and communicative steering feedback. Equipped with four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers and cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal. A driver-focused example with a clean power curve and excellent mechanical synchronization.",
